item.title: [HIVE-8354] HIVE-7156 introduced required dependency on tez
item.description: Should not be much work to fix, but HIVE-7156 introduced a require dep of tez-api.
item.summary: HIVE-7156 introduced required dependency on tez

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.

comments.comment:
This patch removes dependency with DagUtils. It moved the logic for getting map memory to StatsUtils. It really doesn't need yarn's Resource object. The return type is also changed to just return the map memory in mb.

brocknoland Can you take a look at this patch?
